extendedInfo.description: Join us for the 15th Annual Michigan Charter School Conference, November 5 & 6, 2012 at Cobo Hall in Detroit, MI. We are bringing together more than 2,000 charter school educators, over 150 businesses in our revamped exhibit hall, 90+ speakers in charter school specific breakout sessions and two keynote speakers we are sure will inspire you. Join us for two days of high-quality, motivational and educational professional development.Keywords: Michigan Association of Public School Academies, MAPSA, Michigan Charter School Conference
